verses.text: \w O|strong="H3068"\w* \w Jehovah|strong="H3068"\w*, \w our|strong="H5921"\w* Lord, How excellent \w is|strong="H1732"\w* \w thy|strong="H1732"\w* name \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w all|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* earth, Who hast set \w thy|strong="H1732"\w* glory \w upon|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* heavens!

\w Out|strong="H5414"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* mouth \w of|strong="H3068"\w* babes \w and|strong="H3068"\w* sucklings hast \w thou|strong="H5414"\w* \w established|strong="H5414"\w* strength, \w Because|strong="H5921"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w thine|strong="H5414"\w* adversaries, \w That|strong="H3605"\w* \w thou|strong="H5414"\w* mightest still \w the|strong="H3605"\w* enemy \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* avenger.

\w When|strong="H6310"\w* I consider \w thy|strong="H4616"\w* heavens, \w the|strong="H3245"\w* \w work|strong="H3245"\w* \w of|strong="H6310"\w* \w thy|strong="H4616"\w* fingers, \w The|strong="H3245"\w* moon \w and|strong="H6310"\w* \w the|strong="H3245"\w* stars, \w which|strong="H3245"\w* thou hast \w ordained|strong="H3245"\w*;

\w What|strong="H4639"\w* \w is|strong="H4639"\w* \w man|strong="H7200"\w*, \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w thou|strong="H3588"\w* \w art|strong="H4639"\w* mindful \w of|strong="H4639"\w* \w him|strong="H7200"\w*? \w And|strong="H8064"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* son \w of|strong="H4639"\w* \w man|strong="H7200"\w*, \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w thou|strong="H3588"\w* visitest \w him|strong="H7200"\w*?

\w For|strong="H3588"\w* \w thou|strong="H3588"\w* hast \w made|strong="H6485"\w* \w him|strong="H6485"\w* \w but|strong="H3588"\w* little lower \w than|strong="H3588"\w* God, \w And|strong="H1121"\w* crownest \w him|strong="H6485"\w* \w with|strong="H6485"\w* glory \w and|strong="H1121"\w* honor.

Thou makest \w him|strong="H5849"\w* \w to|strong="H3519"\w* \w have|strong="H4592"\w* dominion over \w the|strong="H3519"\w* works \w of|strong="H3519"\w* thy hands; Thou hast put \w all|strong="H2637"\w* things under \w his|strong="H1926"\w* feet:
\w All|strong="H3605"\w* sheep \w and|strong="H3027"\w* oxen, Yea, \w and|strong="H3027"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* beasts \w of|strong="H3027"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* field,

\w The|strong="H3605"\w* birds \w of|strong="H7704"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* heavens, \w and|strong="H7704"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* fish \w of|strong="H7704"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* sea, \w Whatsoever|strong="H3605"\w* passeth \w through|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* paths \w of|strong="H7704"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* seas.

\w O|strong="H3068"\w* \w Jehovah|strong="H3068"\w*, \w our|strong="H5674"\w* Lord, How excellent is \w thy|strong="H5674"\w* name \w in|strong="H3220"\w* \w all|strong="H5674"\w* \w the|strong="H5674"\w* \w earth|strong="H8064"\w*!
